Uses of Class
pec.Event

  • Packages that use Event 
    Package Description
    individual
    Package related to the individuals to be used and the operations they perform or suffer.
    pec
    Package containing the Pending Event Container (PEC) and its respective interface, so that it can be possible to implement the PEC with a different structure or functioning.
    simulation
    Package that contains the items related with the simulation structure, i.e., the abstract class for the grid and our implementation of it, the Point class and the Edge.
